metadata.description: The First Edition Comic NFT is your first entry point into the Omega RUNNER universe. Holding a First Edition NFT grants owners the highest level of access to the project, including first run at The Leaderboard, earning rewards, and presale of the RUNNER Character drop later this year. As the universe grows, this NFT will continue to accrue the most value.
metadata.name: Omega RUNNER x First Edition NFT
